name: iMazing App Data Backup
summary: An IMAZINGAPP file is a backup file created by iMazing, an iPhone backup application. It contains user-specific data (e.g. settings and login information) backed up from an iPhone app. IMAZINGAPP files are named for the app from which they were created (e.g. an IMAZINGAPP file that contains a user's Spotify data is named Spotify.imazingapp).
